e=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\"><img alt=\"House Darry.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/20px-House_Darry.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/30px-House_Darry.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/40px-House_Darry.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/20px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/40px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\"><img alt=\"House Piper.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/20px-House_Piper.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/30px-House_Piper.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/40px-House_Piper.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">House Piper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Roote\" title=\"House Roote\"><img alt=\"House Roote.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a4/House_Roote.svg/20px-House_Roote.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a4/House_Roote.svg/30px-House_Roote.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a4/House_Roote.svg/40px-House_Roote.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Roote\" title=\"House Roote\">House Roote</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Aegon II Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/32px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/48px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/64px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/20px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/40px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/20px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/40px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Bracken\" title=\"Humfrey Bracken\">Humfrey Bracken</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Stone Hedge garrison</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Bracken\" title=\"Humfrey Bracken\">Humfrey Bracken</a> (captured)</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>taking of Stone Hedge</b> occurred near the start of <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Stone_Hedge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a> declared for Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> and her <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> when war broke out, while <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a> supported her half-brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Blackwood\" title=\"Samwell Blackwood\">Samwell Blackwood</a> sent raiders into Bracken lands, so Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Bracken\" title=\"Humfrey Bracken\">Humfrey Bracken</a> sent his son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a>, to retaliate with a strong force. However, Amos was slain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Burning_Mill\" title=\"Battle of the Burning Mill\">Battle of the Burning Mill</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raylon_Rivers\" title=\"Raylon Rivers\">Raylon Rivers</a> led the green survivors back to Bracken territory.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>They returned to <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a> only to find that it had been captured in their absence: Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>, riding his <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Caraxes\" title=\"Caraxes\">Caraxes</a>, had led a strong host of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">Darrys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">Freys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">Pipers</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Roote\" title=\"House Roote\">Rootes</a> to the Brackens' castle. With most of the Bracken forces away with Amos and Raylon, the blacks quickly stormed the castle. Humfrey was captured, along with his remaining children, his third wife, and his lowborn <a href=\"/index.php/Paramour\" title=\"Paramour\">paramour</a>. When Raylon returned to Stone Hedge, he yielded to Daemon, ending any green strength in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Stone_Hedge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Red Dragon and the Gold.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;backgrou